        We reserve the right to update and change the Terms of Service from time to time without
        notice. Any new features that augment or enhance the current Service shall be subject to the
        Terms of Service. Continued use of the Service after any such changes shall constitute your
        consent to such changes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">2. Use License</h2>
